  "title": "Enhanced Celestials",
  "description": "A mod adding new Lunar Events like blood moons and harvest moons!",
  "body": "[<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CorgiTaco/corgitaco.github.io/refs/heads/main/announcement.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">](https://corgitaco.dev/announcement)\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_6b5139da-cb17-45e1-b909-b05a8e5aa823.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"343\">\n\n###### <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_23b05f3e-4687-40db-9422-ab3b2a1dc2ec.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">Enhanced Celestials is a mod that aims to improve the overall environment of the night by adding lunar events such as Blood moons & Harvest moons! Expect fresh lunar content with each coming update!\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_1a53e499-692a-4fd1-9f2b-db20449625a6.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_9bb31d50-27fc-4601-8ffe-44cb03f95d1f.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"659\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_b067a004-12ef-40d0-a07b-fd71a83055d5.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"664\">\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_05a09f15-d0f9-4907-bd8a-0dda7af16d99.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"664\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_20a2d15d-6d67-462a-adea-f013b3c38817.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"664\">\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_9524b473-69d0-4ceb-803b-8d24be11d0ea.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_37825e7a-cc00-4a59-92a5-007f8c86f87a.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/corgilib) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_2abb5d7e-2aa3-487f-a91c-598755cee93e.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/data-anchor)\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_039e8e25-4ae2-4bf6-8d6d-2dfb6e3915a0.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">\n\nMods that enhance compatibility with others mods. For example, shader support.\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_15780d5a-bed6-4d9b-b64a-489417ac9ffb.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enhanced-celestials-shader-support)\n\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_16ec73a1-05a0-4b13-ad90-5c0993241da5.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"100\">\n\nAdd-ons created by the community for this mod!\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_947f74e7-9d0c-48cd-8e86-f426320ac94f.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/horde-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_77cdf2e9-8a75-4d0d-b3ca-921abf483dc7.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ender-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_ee5566b1-3c5b-4f25-9dd0-0e7e9dfbbd00.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/black-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_9a0b25ac-00b3-4fe1-af3f-951a11eedb19.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/spider-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_598f50e4-3f5c-4c07-ac41-d138460b4e09.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/miners-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_bb5dfd82-edfd-4678-9f3c-0e568c1b324b.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/kaboom-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_3bb89075-d182-45f3-a9de-5ea3d29580aa.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/hunters-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_d2335af6-782f-4b8f-94a5-8e37e1a10be5.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chaos-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_71a69fbe-42ba-4358-8239-c6722d908bf1.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/baby-horde-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_7684f507-16be-4346-9453-f4d878a7f746.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extreme-horde-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_ee9c60cd-a8d5-45a0-b100-c25fe5df1f76.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/peaceful-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_74fd7d14-2e83-4080-83eb-edd6f458e6a1.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/peaceful-harvest-and-blue-moons) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_a72ab8c2-47af-4c70-bc11-af0545d00ef5.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/snipers-moon) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_04bb13f4-c1f3-472a-ac0b-3ae9ea3120d0.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\">](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/destructive-moon)\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_425b7799-7b7a-4249-aea7-493751ca76f4.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"200\">](https://github.com/CorgiTaco-MC/Enhanced-Celestials/wiki)\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_a5ad4f9f-fdf1-4281-9f87-9cbdd8171db9.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"104\">](https://www.patreon.com/cw/CorgiTaco) [<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_4180590d-9336-4ada-b338-fc493b7dd222.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"104\">](https://linktr.ee/Corgi_Taco)\n\n[<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/438447/description_2e678191-4f3b-4b31-9667-3417c82a63a1.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"200\">](https://discord.gg/Qfzyh7mynz)",
